(!I)yscroll(!i) !! ~
(!I)cyscroll(!i) !! ~
(!I)cursorpos(!i) !! ~
(!I)cx(!i) !! ~
(!I)cy(!i) !! ~
!end_table

!item [(!nolink [Return]) value:]
The function does not return a result.

!item [Availability:]
